dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. North is oriented to the left. Illustrations include a dog, compass, and coat of arms around the scale cartouche and fruit around the title cartouche. From the Composite Atlas of France, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 36 x 48 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dct_creator_sm: Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner Composite Atlas of France.
